libcotp
------------------------------------------
C library that generates TOTP and HOTP according to RFC-6238

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.4.10-1
  libcotp-devel-3.0.0-1bl1
  libcotp3-3.0.0-1bl1
  libgcrypt20-1.10.3-1
  pkg-config-2.1.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.41-3
  cmake-3.25.3-1
  cygport-0.36.7-1
  gcc-core-11.4.0-1
  libgcrypt-devel-1.10.3-1
  ninja-1.11.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/paolostivanin/libcotp

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/paolostivanin/libcotp/archive/refs/tags/v3.0.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libcotp-3.0.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libcotp-3.0.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libcotp-3.0.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libcotp-3.0.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libcotp3-3.0.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libcotp-devel-3.0.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libcotp)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libcotp.README
  /usr/share/doc/libcotp/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/libcotp/README.md
  /usr/share/doc/libcotp/SECURITY.md

(libcotp3)
  /usr/bin/cygcotp-3.dll

(libcotp-devel)
  /usr/include/cotp.h
  /usr/lib/libcotp.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/cotp.pc

------------------

